{"tid":1710184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會仲有12日代表咩？","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:10:26.000Z","uid":184385,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d8f05d59fb91dea76b60eaf47a5ee43bd8eca9","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"八婆的陰謀都好清楚，利用警犬持續挑釁我地，衝突升溫，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將必敗的區議會選舉延後或取消，</span></span>唔比民意進入制度內部，咁佢要應付的就只係街頭的衝突，由得市民鬥市民，制度內仍然係佢既人。<br />\n<br />\n最近D狗的表現咁失控好明顯係上層有心縱容<br />\n淋病宜家日日話「睇唔到必要延後區議會」，係想我地輕率，錯判形勢。<br />\n<br />\n屌我仲信制度既人，你地問心，覺唔覺得香港人真係有「革命奪權，獨立成邦」的決心？成五個月，大家心照啦。既然係咁，依場持久戰，我地必需利用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">選舉制度</span></span>的力量<br />\n<br />\nBe Water, 街頭係手足，區選都係手足，裡應外合。今年，記住民建聯已經係無撚得自動當選。區議會立法會選舉係彭彭比我地香港人的最後禮物。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我知實會比人屌，但我唔係叫大家抖，唔好街戰或者唔罷工，但大家除左義憤，都要冷靜睇住個日曆做人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">區選仲有12日</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以，和理非！你地咪撚停呀！繼續遊行繼續集會！唔好比哂d責任勇武！新聞有既唔可以只係衝突畫面！<br />\n<br />\n記住，永遠選擇令敵人最麻煩的戰略。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">血債血償</span></span>,<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係唔夠架</span></span>"},{"pid":"69db97b8f444e6236128880ad02ef481d9ace239","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99d83c728dfdca2da6f137367de0f4115892152b","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e34d09adbdcbf671a336e0c036e14c3d74998135","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"就快咳死"},{"pid":"8b85f252f72b07fee04ec4f6bc17db4a30b93422","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"好撚想打爆陳家佩"},{"pid":"9b3fafc91f2e581214f132e995b1cb6170cfd029","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"3b801a91841e033d6285210eab9e73b11c76f11b","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"今朝無出到去，sor9各位"},{"pid":"b387e5db10da86dc151390fb97111ee841dbe76a","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"已經好耐無5點起身"},{"pid":"5a94497692ef96cd8f11f405e0840cfd463dbe44","tid":1710184,"uid":184385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"一日都已經有點暈"},{"pid":"32371b477335c4578511606d04f0f29eacd3f15f","tid":1710184,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"成日講佢會取消區會<br />\n<br />\n我反而想知，取消之後，有無法理依據處理現時區會議員議席係會無限期連任，定係會無人上任？"},{"pid":"a3329345550e3ac89f3d33dcededa43b694c5104","tid":1710184,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0822135ab7ce0f8e890bd78731e7e69b837a805a","tid":1710184,"uid":116000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6c6ec8d1465cb41014fc1cddf338c07cf2e7890","tid":1710184,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"區選成績 半數議席都贏唔到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724079</a>"}]}